Good day friends! Another candid photo of King Ronnie just chillin...with guns just hanging!!! It's been a few years since I had what anyone would call 'decent' guns but it's a good feeling...especially when you train them and the pump gets so painful you can barely lift your hand to your face!! Yes, I must admit I miss them...but I don't miss all those meals I had to eat to keep them that size!! Who'd have thought eating would be hard work? Ask any top bodybuilder and I think they'll tell you eating is the hardest part of it all...that and the cooking, cleaning and prepping lol!! Three meals is more than enough now!!
